      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "WRITE (create/update/delete):\n  Client → Controller → ZodValidationPipe\n  → Service (regra negócio: unicidade, FK)\n  → Repository → SQL Server\n  → cache.delByPrefix('brands:page:') ou del('vehicle:id')\n  → 201/200/204\n\nREAD (findAll):\n  Client → Controller → Service\n  → cache.get('brands:page:1:20')\n  → HIT: retorna cache\n  → MISS: Repository → SQL → cache.set(TTL)\n\nCache backend:\n  USE_MEMORY_CACHE=true → MemoryCacheService\n  else → RedisCacheService (ioredis)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "flow",
      "originalText": "WRITE (create/update/delete):\n  Client → Controller → ZodValidationPipe\n  → Service (regra negócio: unicidade, FK)\n  → Repository → SQL Server\n  → cache.delByPrefix('brands:page:') ou del('vehicle:id')\n  → 201/200/204\n\nREAD (findAll):\n  Client → Controller → Service\n  → cache.get('brands:page:1:20')\n  → HIT: retorna cache\n  → MISS: Repository → SQL → cache.set(TTL)\n\nCache backend:\n  USE_MEMORY_CACHE=true → MemoryCacheService\n  else → RedisCacheService (ioredis)",
